narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I learned about a variety of topics that are important a graduate student other than the research.
I learned a variety of ethical issues relating to many aspects of scientific research.
I learned a lot in this course pertaining to proper research techniques and how to handle issues that may arise.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I enjoyed the class and the topics covered were relevant.
I enjoyed that the course was very discussion based, but smaller group discussion might get more people involved.
I think that some of the instructors were amazing and others were okay, but overall this course was much better than the one offered in the fall.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes, I would recommend to the first year student.
Yes...? It's a required class obviously, but everything covered is relevant and the class addressed issues that I had previously not dealt with.
